In SQLite
- column names are not case-sensitive
- use `--`, `/* */` to comment out
- `FROM TABLE1 INNER JOIN TABLE2 USING (ColumnName1)` or `FROM TABLE1 INNER JOIN TABLE2 ON ColumnName1 = ColumnName2`
- correct comment syntax
    -- `--` is followed by a space or newline
    -- comments are placed outside SQL keywords
